com.objetdirect.tatami.client.grid
Class Cell

java.lang.Object
  com.objetdirect.tatami.client.grid.Cell
All Implemented Interfaces:
ConvertibleToJSObject
public class Cell
extends java.lang.Object
implements ConvertibleToJSObject

This class represents a cell. A cell defines an area of data in a grid. It is the atomic entity in the grid layout. A cell content can be defined in two ways : - a field name : if a field name is specified, the cell will be filled with the same named attribute in the grid data store - no field name and a default value : the cell content will be constant a cell content can contain HTML.

Author:
rdunklau
